title: Stimulus, Tax Credits, 2020, Rep. Westerman

description:
Guests: Jordan Fabian, Bloomberg White House reporter, Former Florida Congressman Patrick Murphy, Adam Goodman, Republican media strategist, columnist and partner at Ballard Partners in Washington, Congressman Bruce Westerman, a Republican representing Arkansas's 4th district, and Jack Fitzpatrick, Bloomberg Government Congressional reporter.
